### Get the list of all specials
GET {{baseURL}}/api/Specials

### Creates a new special
POST {{baseURL}}/api/Specials
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "DateTime": "2026-04-15T08:00:00Z",
  "Name": "Test special 8:00 AM"
}

### Updates the specified special
PUT {{baseURL}}/api/Specials/3
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "DateTime": "2026-04-15T09:00:00Z",
  "Name": "Test special 9:00 AM"
}

### Deletes the specified special
DELETE {{baseURL}}/api/Specials/3
